@startuml UEORMS_State_13
top to bottom direction
hide empty description
title UEORMS State Transition - 12) Governance and Compliance

[*] --> PolicyDraft
PolicyDraft --> PolicyApproved : review approved
PolicyDraft --> PolicyRejected : review rejected
PolicyRejected --> PolicyDraft : update and resubmit

PolicyApproved --> ControlMapped : map controls to modules
ControlMapped --> EvidenceCollection : start evidence cycle
EvidenceCollection --> ComplianceCheck : run compliance checks
ComplianceCheck --> Compliant : all checks pass
ComplianceCheck --> NonCompliant : findings detected

NonCompliant --> RemediationPlanned : assign remediation
RemediationPlanned --> RemediationInProgress : execute remediation
RemediationInProgress --> RecheckPending : remediation complete
RecheckPending --> ComplianceCheck : re-run checks

Compliant --> AuditReady : compile audit package
AuditReady --> AuditClosed : audit accepted
AuditClosed --> [*]

@enduml
